   ```
   sqlplus / as sysdba
   ```

2. Tạo quyền cho role:
   ```sql
   SQL> create role RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE;
   SQL> grant connect, resource, create view to RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE;
   ```

3. Tạo user cho từng tablespace cần import:
   ```sql
   create user ACS_RS identified by PASSWORD;
   create user HIS_RS identified by PASSWORD;
   create user SAR_RS identified by PASSWORD;
   create user SDA_RS identified by PASSWORD;
   create user LIS_RS identified by PASSWORD;
   create user QCS_RS identified by PASSWORD;
   create user QCU_RS identified by PASSWORD;
   ```

4. Gán quyền cho các user đã tạo:
   ```sql
   grant "RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE" to "ACS_RS";
   grant "RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE" to "HIS_RS";
   grant "RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE" to "SAR_RS";
   grant "RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE" to "SDA_RS";
   grant "RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE" to "LIS_RS";
   grant "RAW_SCHEMA_ROLE" to "QCS_RS";
